e is coadministered with a moderate inhibitor of CYP450 3A4.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/109511/', '', 'Ciclesonide, Umeclidinium, Mometasone furoate, Aclidinium, Glycopyrronium, Flunisolide, Ipratropium, Cromoglicic acid, Revefenacin, Nedocromil, Tiotropium, More', '', 1767369485);
